The paper proposes a generative model for adversarial attack on CNN, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the security implications of adversarial attacks, which could be relevant to the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the use of generative models suggests a potential connection to the category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
